      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Seriously, it's in such incredible shape that it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with its care\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure driving perfection. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
